title: Rediscover [4 Albums + 5 Extra Tracks]
description:
Rediscover is a power/synth pop band from Toledo, Ohio. Originally started as a solo project by Wes Quinonez in 2004, it has now expanded to a full band with drummer, Rob Wagner, guitarist, Mikey Corwin, and bassist, Daaron Davis.

Albums:

160~190kbps [2004] The Ocean Is Calling Us [EP]
160~224kbps [2005] Out Of Touch [EP]
192~256kbps [2006] Call Me When You Get This [EP]
~~~~224kbps [2008] Sleepless Nights

~190kbps Rediscover - Not Giving In
~256kbps Rediscover - One Eighty
